---------------------------------------------------
|0 |MERGE GROUP BY          |      |0        |84  |
|1 | SORT                   |      |0        |84  |
|2 |  NESTED-LOOP CONNECT BY|      |0        |84  |
|3 |   TABLE SCAN           |tgroup|5        |37  |
|4 |   MATERIAL             |      |5        |39  |
|5 |    TABLE SCAN          |tgroup|5        |37  |
===================================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([T_FUN_COUNT(1)]), filter(nil), 
      group([tgroup.c1]), agg_func([T_FUN_COUNT(1)])
  1 - output([tgroup.c1]), filter(nil), sort_keys([tgroup.c1, ASC])
  2 - output([tgroup.c1]), filter(nil), 
      conds([tgroup.c1 = tgroup.c2]), nl_params_(nil)
  3 - output([tgroup.c1], [tgroup.c2]), filter(nil), 
      access([tgroup.c1], [tgroup.c2]), partitions(p0)
